title: Paradox supremacy LF Jungler plat 3 +  (for main roster)   and Manager for team

embed.description: Step up your game with a modern voice & text chat app. Crystal clear voice, multiple server and channel support, mobile apps, and more. Get your free server now!

body:
Hey guys

Must be willing to learn, accept feedback and play co-operativly with team and commit to scrims at least 3 times a week (18:30 onward NSW time)

for a trial 
PM IGN: Isotope   
or PM IGN: Ich0r
